      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ibn Mahboub, from Ibn Ri’ab, from Abu Ubeyda Al Haza’a, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup style=\"font-weight: normal\">asws</sup> having said: ‘It is an Obligation for the <span class=\"iTxt\">Momin</span> upon the <span class=\"iTxt\">Momin</span>, the advice’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Ibn Mahbub has narrated from ibn Ri’ab from abu ‘Ubaydah al-Hadhdha’ from abu Ja’far (a.s.) who has said the following: “It is of a believer’s obligations to provide good advice to another believer.” "
        ]
      }
